name: Create a published post using new button

elements.name: As a user I create a published post using New post button on posts list

steps.name: I set scenario "Post_creation_published" and version app "3.3.0"
I enter "<USER>" into input field having id "ember8"
I enter "<PASSWORD>" into input field having id "ember10"
I click on element having id "ember12"
I click on element having xpath "//a[@class='ember-view'][2]"
